title: Art in Small-Scale Societies (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
Art in Small-Scale Societies
Prentice Hall | 1989 | ISBN: 0130477621 | English | 242 pages | PDF | 39.2 MB

Core text that discusses the major questions regarding art in its cultural context. Based on fieldwork studies of hunter-gatherer, horticultural and pastoral peoples from around the word. For courses in primitive art in departments of anthropology and art history
